body:
Hello again @achowdhery :)
As you probably remember from [here](https://github.com/tensorflow/models/issues/5020) I am still not able to build .tflite file, so I decided to user Tensorflow Mobile with frozen graph instead of ml-kit, as it was in the [article](https://medium.com/tensorflow/training-and-serving-a-realtime-mobile-object-detector-in-30-minutes-with-cloud-tpus-b78971cf1193)
So, I successfully built the demo project with Android Studio as it was described in this [tutorial](https://www.tensorflow.org/mobile/android_build) and TF Classify works great, but I need TF Detect. And with enabling TF Detect demo I faced the same problem that guys above T____T
I really hope there is some solution for at least on of these issues...
